###awesome-minecraft

The awesome list *awesome-minecraft* lists many awesome things in the world of Minecraft. Currently listed subjects include mods, maps, mod loaders, modded clients, and resource packs.

See the list at [Armored-Dragon/awesome-minecraft](https://github.com/Armored-Dragon/awesome-minecraft)!
